The subroutine here is built based on the postprocess_fluid_stats subroutine: https://github.com/ExtremeFLOW/neko/contrib/postprocess_fluid_stats

To use this postprocessing subroutine, first install the classical Neko: https://github.com/ExtremeFLOW/neko

Follow the instruction of install Neko

Replace the postprocess_fluid_stats file under /neko/contrib/ with the one here

Replace the fluid_stats.f90 file under /neko/src/fluid/ with the one here

Compile by 'make' or 'makeinstall'

Instruction of using the subroutine can be found in 'readme'
